abstract: |
  A high-performance B-Tree index construction engine (Order 4) implemented in Rust with 
  Persian character normalization and natural sorting. Compliant with ISO/IEC 10646 (Unicode) 
  and ISO/IEC 25010 (software quality). Visualized in WebAssembly (Dioxus) for 
  client-side browser execution.

